prompt: How do I reset my password and set up Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) on the video editor platform?
response: To reset your password and set up MFA on the video editor platform, follow these steps: First, go to the 'Settings' tab within the application. Next, click on 'Password' and follow the prompts to reset your current password. After successfully changing your password, navigate back to the settings and select 'Security'. Here, you can enable MFA by choosing from available options such as SMS codes or authenticator apps. Follow the on-screen instructions for completion.
